  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136170/extras/416c46421bdd5614a9938dfde3073c53.avif?t=1665441036\" width=532 height=74 /></span><br><br><i>Accompany Maya, a mysterious hooded woman, and her little companion on an adventure where the only thing that matters is reaching the top.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136170/extras/51353c8355e4bc094aabfe135020f3f9.avif?t=1665441036\" width=532 height=74 /></span><br><br><strong>GET TO THE TOP</strong><br><br>To The Top is a randomly generated 2D platform game with pixel style artwork.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  <strong>Move, Shoot and Use Power Ups</strong> to reach the top of each level while battling and dogging your enemies. <br></li><li>  Do your best to finish each level an get the <strong>code</strong> to access each scenario! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136170/extras/ac7af1b219127495fd7f66b2f00db548.avif?t=1665441036\" width=532 height=74 /></span><br><br>Enjoy the <strong>music of the talented Jake Altmann</strong> as you progress through this dangerous futuristic world in either Casual or Normal mode.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136170/extras/416c46421bdd5614a9938dfde3073c53.avif?t=1665441036\" width=532 height=74 /></span><br><br><i>Accompany Maya, a mysterious hooded woman, and her little companion on an adventure where the only thing that matters is reaching the top.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136170/extras/51353c8355e4bc094aabfe135020f3f9.avif?t=1665441036\" width=532 height=74 /></span><br><br><strong>GET TO THE TOP</strong><br><br>To The Top is a randomly generated 2D platform game with pixel style artwork.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  <strong>Move, Shoot and Use Power Ups</strong> to reach the top of each level while battling and dogging your enemies. <br></li><li>  Do your best to finish each level an get the <strong>code</strong> to access each scenario! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136170/extras/ac7af1b219127495fd7f66b2f00db548.avif?t=1665441036\" width=532 height=74 /></span><br><br>Enjoy the <strong>music of the talented Jake Altmann</strong> as you progress through this dangerous futuristic world in either Casual or Normal mode.</li></ul>",
